{
  "stem": "20405.6",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So they cut the wires, because it was preparing for that, for that [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They cut the wires, the electrical wires.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they start to run out, everybody on the-- there was too many trees.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "What they call them?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The forest.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On the forest.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because after the forest, over there, in about maybe 10 kilometers, or five kilometers, or 15 kilometers, there was another guard of Germans.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were running out from there, the crematorium one.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The crematorium two, we couldn't do nothing, because they [? circled ?] us right away.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Surrounded from the Germans, yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] We were preparing for those, all those things, one of the Russian-- Malenkov, Malenkov-- one of those Russians of the 18, Malenkov name-- a very strong guy, tall.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What he did-- he went, he punch the two wheels of the bicycle the German, not to let him get out and call for help.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In the meantime, we were [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When the Germans came-- the Germans, I told you, was a red one, who was asking-- who was working as a Sonderkommando in Mauthausen.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's the same German.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He got his cane.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he ask, who punch his bicycle?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he said, I did.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And with the cane, he killed him, with the cane-- hit him on his head.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that was the end of this Malenkov.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "In the meantime, crematorium one, over there was this kapo, the German, [INAUDIBLE] the name, which was one of the worst kapos we ever had over there, beating to everybody for nothing, just passing by by him, with the cane, bam, on your head.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "A couple guys of us-- two, three guys of us-- they got him.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They knife him-- right away, on the oven.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "That was the end of this [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
